  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK189">
<l>aṟaṉōkki yāṟṟuṅkol vaiyam puṟaṉōkkip</l>
<l>puṉco luraippāṉ poṟai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The world through charity supports the weight of those who reproach others observing their absence.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
